00:20.580 --> 00:22.548
Emily, come on!

00:22.590 --> 00:24.182
Heads up!

00:24.220 --> 00:26.381
It's yours.

00:26.420 --> 00:28.217
Hey, guys.

00:28.260 --> 00:29.579
