01:26.680 --> 01:28.477
When did you
figure out it was me?

01:28.520 --> 01:30.408
Days ago.

01:30.450 --> 01:32.657
You kept coming to see me.

01:32.690 --> 01:34.681
Insinuating things.

01:34.720 --> 01:37.382
Look, I just wanted you
to confess, not this.

01:38.560 --> 01:41.688
I didn't want to kill Yanis.

01:41.730 --> 01:43.368
