01:44.470 --> 01:46.358
for crying out loud.
(phone chimes)

01:50.610 --> 01:51.804
What are you...?

01:51.840 --> 01:53.239
Shush.

01:54.340 --> 01:55.568
He's struck again.

01:55.610 --> 01:56.679
VVho?

01:56.710 --> 01:58.678
The Bensonhurst Bomber.

01:58.710 --> 02:00.211
Do you remember him?

02:00.250 --> 02:01.842
A serial bomber.

02:01.880 --> 02:03.518
An affinity for putting
improvised explosives

02:03.550 --> 02:05.313
in-in random places.

02:05.350 --> 02:08.319
His original reign of terror
was the bulk of 2010,

02:08.360 --> 02:09.349
and then he just disappeared.

02:09.390 --> 02:12.188
No one heard from him
for srx years.

02:12.230 --> 02:15.358
And then, several weeks ago, he
set off a device in a food court

02:15.400 --> 02:17.425
