a group of teenagers.

02:17.470 --> 02:19.859
He just...
just killed a man.

02:19.900 --> 02:22.539
We have to go.

02:22.570 --> 02:23.764
I'm not going anywhere.

02:23.810 --> 02:25.334
Not talking to you.

02:25.370 --> 02:26.337
Huh?

02:26.380 --> 02:29.133
(Taser crackling)

02:32.620 --> 02:34.212
Took you long enough.

02:34.250 --> 02:36.445
You couldn't get him
further away from the ledge?

02:36.490 --> 02:38.481
(exhales)

02:42.830 --> 02:46.288
(sirens wailing, urgent chatter)

02:46.330 --> 02:48.389
GREGSON: Looks like the bomb
was a homemade device.

02:48.430 --> 02:51.319
Composed mostly of bleach
and potassium chloride.

02:51.370 --> 02:53.292
Bensonhurst Bomber's
srgnature recrpe.

