08:21.830 --> 08:25.163
Where were you on, uh,
Tuesday, April 2, 2010,

08:25.200 --> 08:27.259
uh, 10:40 in the morning?

08:27.300 --> 08:29.165
I was at the Whitechapel Gallery
in London

08:29.200 --> 08:31.168
_at an exhibition_ _
of neonmpressnonlst painting.

