90% of my job is running around
the city, going to build sites.

08:39.080 --> 08:41.014
Most of my days,
my schedule's shot to hell

08:41.050 --> 08:42.711
before I finish my coffee.

08:42.750 --> 08:45.639
Even if I found my calendar
from 2010,

08:45.690 --> 08:47.214
