know someone in common.

10:09.200 --> 10:10.861
(grunting)

10:12.840 --> 10:17.004
MAN:
Stick and move.
Stick and move!

10:17.050 --> 10:20.213
BOXER:
Felon.

10:20.250 --> 10:22.741
Hey, felon, don't act
like you don't hear me.

10:22.790 --> 10:24.985
