the two of you worked together

12:15.100 --> 12:17.819
in the prison
cafeteria.

12:17.870 --> 12:19.792
I remember him.

12:19.840 --> 12:21.068
Were you close?

12:21.100 --> 12:22.169
Why?

12:22.200 --> 12:23.531
A bomb went off in a park

12:23.570 --> 12:24.798
