12:40.360 --> 12:41.952
Okay.

12:44.160 --> 12:47.095
So, you've been out
for the past few weeks, right?

12:47.130 --> 12:49.223
How's it going?

12:49.260 --> 12:52.263
Well, I live in a halfway house.

12:52.300 --> 12:57.328
I empty buckets of spit
for a living...

12:58.610 --> 13:00.430
...but I could be dead.

13:00.480 --> 13:04.200
You know that better
than anybody.

13:09.550 --> 13:11.814
You think of anything.

13:18.430 --> 13:21.251
It's good to see you.

13:32.270 --> 13:34.602
(indistinct conversation)

13:34.640 --> 13:37.438
(keys beeping)

13:39.410 --> 13:40.616
Yeah, it's me.

13:40.650 --> 13:42.345
I know you said never
to call you,

13:42.380 --> 13:44.280
