very convenient accident.

15:14.110 --> 15:15.270
All right, say you're right.

15:15.310 --> 15:17.073
I burned a building down.

15:17.110 --> 15:18.941
What the hell would that have
to do with setting off bombs?

15:18.980 --> 15:20.948
Perhaps you liked the way
it felt.

15:20.980 --> 15:23.210
